Source: pglock
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/fraruiz/pglock

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pglock
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pglock
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${postgresql:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION-cron
Description: Lightweight distributed lock service inside PostgreSQL
  pglock implements a lightweight distributed lock service using SQL functions,
  a lock table, and TTL cleanup scheduled through pg_cron.
